<p class="fs-5">Hello <%= @resource.email %>!</p>

<p class="mb-2">Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.</p>

<p class="mb-4"><%= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: 'btn btn-primary' %></p>

<p>If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.</p>
<p class="mb-4">Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.</p>
